  <main id="main" role="main">
    <section id="about" class="content-section reveal-on-scroll" aria-labelledby="aboutTitle">
      <h2 id="aboutTitle">Empowering Healthcare Through Progressive Innovation</h2>
      <p class="lead">World-class medicine should feel accessible. InnoGen advances high-quality generics for the Philippines with a science-first, life-valuing mission.</p>

      <div class="story-grid" role="list" aria-label="About highlights">
        <div class="story-card" role="listitem">
          <div class="story-kicker">Access</div>
          <div class="story-title">Affordable medicine.</div>
          <p>Quality and affordability designed to reach more patients in the Philippines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-card" role="listitem">
          <div class="story-kicker">Quality</div>
          <div class="story-title">FDA-aligned standards.</div>
          <p>Manufacturing discipline and Philippine FDA requirements guide every product.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-card" role="listitem">
          <div class="story-kicker">Portfolio</div>
          <div class="story-title">Therapeutic reach.</div>
          <p>From cardiovascular and metabolic care to infectious disease and respiratory wellness.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-card" role="listitem">
          <div class="story-kicker">Innovation</div>
          <div class="story-title">Technology-forward.</div>
          <p>Continuous improvement in drug manufacturing and scientific capability.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <details class="deep-copy">
        <summary>Read full About Us</summary>
        <div class="deep-copy-body">
          <p>InnoGen Pharmaceuticals, Inc. stands at the forefront of the healthcare industry in the Philippines, driven by a singular mission: to provide the next generation of pharmaceutical solutions that value life above all. As a dynamic player in the local landscape, we specialize in the innovation of generic medications, ensuring that high-quality, life-saving treatments remain cost-effective and accessible to every Filipino.</p>

          <h3>Who We Are</h3>
          <p><strong>InnoGen Pharmaceuticals Inc.</strong> is a company that makes a difference in the pharmaceutical industry, because its thrust is geared towards improving existing products into new forms that are cost-effective but of excellent quality—benefiting the welfare of end-users.</p>
          <p><strong>InnoGen Pharmaceuticals Inc.</strong> resulted from the fusion of nine Filipino-owned pharmaceutical companies, initiated in June 2010. From different therapeutic classes, our areas of concentration include the Cardio-Metabolic Division, CNS and Gastro Division, and the Anti-infectives and Respiratory Division, supported by ethical marketing and promotions on a national coverage.</p>
          <p><strong>InnoGen Pharmaceuticals Inc.</strong> is proud to be the first national company that has provided second-to-innovator pharmaceutical products, most of which are off-patent molecules.</p>
          <p><strong>InnoGen Pharmaceuticals Inc.</strong> has spearheaded technology transfer and partnerships with pharmaceutical companies around the world, enabling access to the latest information and facilities in the industry.</p>

          <h3>Mission</h3>
          <p>To develop and provide quality, innovative and affordable pharmaceutical products for the Filipinos and people around the globe.</p>

          <h3>Vision</h3>
          <p>To become the leader in the Philippine pharmaceutical market and be a globally-competitive pharmaceutical company that would be known in technological innovations in the drug manufacturing field.</p>

          <h3>Our Core Values</h3>
          <ul class="values-list">
            <li>Commitment</li>
            <li>Customer Focus</li>
            <li>Entrepreneurial Excellence</li>
            <li>Health &amp; Wellness</li>
            <li>Integrity</li>
            <li>Practicality</li>
            <li>Respect</li>
            <li>Unity</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Our Commitment to Quality</h3>
          <p>At InnoGen, we believe that "generic" should never mean "compromised." Our research and development team focuses on improving existing product formulations to enhance efficacy and patient compliance. We adhere to the most stringent global manufacturing standards and local regulatory requirements set by the Philippine Food and Drug Administration (FDA). This dedication to excellence ensures that every capsule and tablet bearing the InnoGen name is a product of scientific integrity and trusted expertise.</p>

          <h3>Expanding Therapeutic Reach</h3>
          <p>Our diverse portfolio covers a wide range of therapeutic classes, addressing the most pressing health challenges in the region—from cardiovascular health and metabolic care to infectious diseases and respiratory wellness. By bridging the gap between advanced pharmaceutical science and daily healthcare needs, we empower doctors and patients with reliable alternatives to expensive innovator brands.</p>

          <h3>A Future-Ready Direction</h3>
          <p>We are more than just a pharmaceutical supplier; we are a partner in the Philippine healthcare ecosystem. Through continuous investment in modern technology and scientific talent, InnoGen is building a future where world-class medicine is a standard right, not a luxury. We value life, and through our pursuit of pharmaceutical innovation, we are helping the nation breathe, heal, and live better every day.</p>

          <h3>Our Commitment</h3>
          <p>InnoGen Pharmaceuticals, Inc. will continue to be the world-class innovator in healthcare solutions in the service of Filipinos primarily, and for people worldwide in the near future.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </section>

